{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fafc2e8b61","title":"先取朔县宁武再取山阴代品不要惊动傅作义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b094a80ad8","index":0,"year":1946,"month":6,"day":9,"articleId":"fafc2e8b61"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e4a1486f47","type":"paragraph","text":"先取朔县宁武再取山阴代品","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fafc2e8b61"},{"id":"43c5786ad6","type":"paragraph","text":"不要惊动傅作义口","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fafc2e8b61"},{"id":"cb12495177","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年6月9日）贺、李，并告鼓、刘内（一）你们可以同时或先后攻取朔县、宁武两点，得手后再考虑攻取山阴、伤岳两点。（二）对大同、口泉、怀仁三点不去惊动。（三）不要调动北线主力，不要惊动傅作义","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fafc2e8b61"},{"id":"3f8d4ba609","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fafc2e8b61"},{"id":"3b2071a95f","type":"paragraph","text":"已佳[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给番绥军区司令员贺龙和政治委员泰井泉的电报。[2]爱、刘，指爱荣臻、刘洞涛，当时分别任番察雾军区司令员兼政治变员和副政治委员。[3]山阴，指山阴城，位于山西山阴县南部。岱岳，镇名，今为山西山明县县治。A","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fafc2e8b61"}],"page":{"id":"1d34d92fff","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fafc2e8b61","start":379,"end":379}}}},"__N_SSG":true}